\id TIT
\h TAETAS
\toc1 Taetas
\toc2 Taet
\mt1 Taetas
\mt2 Naoa it…ôm Pol t…ôm…ôte tuw…®n k…ôm Taetas
\imt1 N…ôghat…ôn …ôku…ôk…®r r…ôha naoa u Taetas
\ip \bd ?Pah t…ôm…ôte naoa u?\bd* Aposol Pol t…ôm…ôte naoa u.
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte tatuw…®n k…ôm pah?\bd* Pol t…ôm…ôte naoa u tatuw…®n k…ôm Taetas. Taetas in Iaihlu…ô kit it…ôm t…ômahat…ôt…ô e Kristo. Pol t…ômiuw-pa in o Kristo, k…ôn Taetas t…ômol w…ôk tep…ôt ilau Pol tahmen …ôm e Timoti. Koatehm n…ôrg…®n nian tep…ôt e Niutesteman.
\ip \bd ?N…ômeg…ôh…ôn tahro nulan nian t…ôm…ôte?\bd* Pol ne Taetas k…ômian e n…ôpt…ôn u Krit, k…ôn ilau k…ômu…ôtuoun nim…ôfak kit ik…®n-u. Pol t…ômiet m…®n, m…ôto t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm Taetas m…ôm…ô in ot…ôtat…®g mol rafin w…ôk m…®n ik…®n …ôh. Krit in n…ôpt…ôn kit it…ôm t…ôrioah w…®r e nol…ôn rat m…®n, tahmen m…ôm…ô inu net…ômim koateiu…ô p…®k nian rafin, moatagw…ôn p…®k, k…ôn moat…ôlpah koat…ôlpah. Neen koatuwa e nim…ôfak k…ôn moat…ôn n…ôghat…ôn eiu…ô tep…ôt m…ôm…ô okotos m…ôni lan.
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte naoa u o naka?\bd* Pol tolkeike m…ôm…ô otasitu e Taetas e r…ôhan m…®n w…ôk …ôp…ôh e nim…ôfak …ôp…ôh Krit. Taetas ot…ôk…ôike m…®l…ôs-ip…ôr net…ômim m…ôm…ô okotuwa elta m…®n o nehm…ôn nim…ôfak. K…ôn Pol tat…ôghat-in nol…ôn r…ôha n…ôghat…ôn k…ôm net…ôm m…®n u k…ôsot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn…ôn n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôha Taetas. K…ôn mos-ip…ôn n…ôg…ôtun…ôn neen r…ôha nahat…ôt…ô…ôn ne naliw…ôk…ôn …ôtuat…®p. K…ôn in t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô Timoti otahtos…®g-in w…®r n…ôg…ôtun…ôn eiu…ô m…®n. Namnun n…ôghat…ôn t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô otahl-ipa et…ômim kit tuwa masitu e nim…ôfak, k…ôn Taetas in ot…ôk…ôike muwa m…®n masitu e Pol.
\c 1
\s1 Pol t…ôm…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm Taetas
\p 
\v 1 Taetas. Io Pol, iat…ôte naoa u k…ôm ik. Io slef kit r…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôn io aposol kit r…ôha Iesu Kristo. T…ômahl-ipa io m…ôm…ô ekasitu e net…ômim it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…®t…ôpun r…ôk…®s ilat m…ôm…ô r…ôhan m…®n, m…®l…ôs-ip…ôr nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhalat, masitu elat m…ôm…ô okot…®tun n…ôg…ôtun…ôn pahrien. Nian net…ômim koat…ôt…ôu-p…ôn n…ôg…ôtun…ôn pahrien …ôh, k…ôn r…ôhalat n…ômeg…ôh…ôn ot…ôtuat…®p kotahmen-p…ôn e nol…ôn it…ôm Uhg…®n tolkeike.
\v 2 Kitat kot…®tun n…®pahrien…ôn …ôh, k…ôn motahat…ôt…ô lan. K…ôn e nol…ôn …ôh, r…ôhatat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn t…ôtat…®g …ôskas…®k r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô okotos n…ômeg…ôh…ôn lil…®n. Aup…ôn aup…ôn ag…®n it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôsol…ôn …ôh nat…®mnat rafin, m…ôto Uhg…®n t…®n…ôm…ôn r…ôk…®s n…ômeg…ôh…ôn lil…®n …ôh, m…ôm…ô in otol mihin. K…ôn kitat kot…®tun m…ôm…ô in t…ôseiu…ôn nian kit ne.\x - \xo 1:2 \xt Kol 1:27 \x*
\v 3 K…ôn e nian …ôtuat…®p it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn, in t…ômol m…ôm…ô net…ômim okot…®tun n…ôghat…ôn r…ôhan. Ilat kot…®tun m…ôto-inu Uhg…®n Iosmeg…ôh r…ôhatat t…ôm…ôn m…ôl…ôh…ôu n…ôghat…ôn kit m…ôm…ô t…ômos-ipa w…ôk u t…ôtat…®g e nelm…ôk m…ôm…ô io ek…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn …ôh r…ôha n…ômeg…ôh…ôn lil…®n.
\p 
\v 4 Taetas, r…ôhalau nahat…ôt…ô…ôn kiti…ôh, k…ôn e nol…ôn r…ôha nahat…ôt…ô…ôn, in tahmen …ôm m…ô ik n…ôt…®k pahrien. R…ôhak n…ôfak…ôn m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n Tata r…ôhatat ilau Kristo Iesu, Iosmeg…ôh r…ôhatat, p…ôs okuawte-in r…ôhalau n…ôw…®r…ôn k…ôm ik, k…ôn mu…ôl…ôh…ôu n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn t…ôtat…®g ron ik.\x - \xo 1:4 \xt Rom 1:7; 2 Kor 8:23; Kal 2:3 \x*
\s1 W…ôk r…ôha Taetas …ôp…ôh Krit
\p 
\v 5 E nian emiet Krit, k…ôn em…ôl…ôh…ôu ik n…ôk…ôtat…®g m…ôm…ô on…ôkol rafin w…ôk it…ôm t…ôtat…®g, k…ôn m…ôm…ô onak…®l…ôs-ip…ôr elta m…®n r…ôha nim…ôfak, e taon m…®n rafin e n…®t…ôn Krit tahmen …ôm m…ô inu em…ôn mihin k…ôm ik.
\v 6 Elta m…®n r…ôha nim…ôfak ok…ôike k…ôsehm-p…ôn…ôn nol…ôn rat kit e r…ôhalat n…ômeg…ôh…ôn, k…ôn r…ôhalat p…ôtan kiti…ôh …ôm, k…ôn r…ôhalat n…®sualk…ôl…ôh okot…ôk…ôike motahat…ôt…ô e Uhg…®n, k…ôn m…ôsotan …ôpnap…®n…ôn motol nat…®mnat t…ôsahmen…ôn, k…ôn m…ôsot…ôht…ôn n…ôwia r…ôhalat tata ne mama m…ôm…ô net…ômim okot…ôn rat ilat ron.
\v 7 N…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôha elta m…®n r…ôha nim…ôfak ot…ôk…ôike m…ôtuat…®p w…®r m…ôto-inu ilat koatos w…ôk asol r…ôha Uhg…®n. Ilat it…ôm koatehm w…®r net…ômim okot…ôk…ôike motol mihin m…ôm…ô k…ôsot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr at…®p…ôn ilat motol r…ôhalat n…ôghat…ôn m…ôm…ô net…ômim okot…ôgin, k…ôn n…®kilat t…ôsahm…ô u…ôhai…ôn. S…ôn…ôm…ô ilat net…ômim r…ôha nap…®s…ôn o n…ômou…ôn, k…ôn s…ôn…ôm…ô ilat net…ômim r…ôha nos…ôn m…ôni e neiueiu…ô…ôn.
\p 
\v 8 M…ôto n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhalat in ot…ôk…ôike mol min-nulan. Ilat okot…ôk…ôike moatehm w…®r net…ômim it…ôm koatuwa …ôh r…ôhalat ik…®n. Ilat net…ôm kotolkeike m…ô okotol …ôm nat…®mnat it…ôm t…ôw…®r, k…ôn nol…ôn r…ôhalat in tat…ôg…ôtun m…ô ilat net…ôm m…ôt…ô, k…ôn kotenat…®g. Ilat net…ôm r…ôha n…ôt…ôu-p…ôn…ôn n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n. R…ôhalat n…ômeg…ôh…ôn in ot…ôk…ôike m…ôtuat…®p w…®r e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n. Ilat kot…®tun n…ôn at…®p…ôn e n…®kilat m…ôm…ô kotap…ôs nol…ôn nat…®mnat it…ôm t…ôrat k…ôn moatol …ôm nat it…ôm t…ôw…®r.
\v 9 Ilat okot…ôk…ôike motahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô in n…®pahrien…ôn tahmen-p…ôn m…ô k…ôm…ôg…ôtun ilat lan. K…ôn in…ôh, ilat kotenat…®g w…®r o n…ôg…ôtun…ôn net…ômim e n…ôg…ôtun…ôn pahrien it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p m…ôm…ô ilat okot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn. K…ôn nian net…ômim neen okoat…ôn n…ôghat…ôn m…®n it…ôm tol p…®s…®n e n…ôg…ôtun…ôn pahrien, k…ôn net…ôm-iasol m…®n r…ôha nim…ôfak okot…ôg…ôtun …ôtuat…®p ilat mot…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô r…ôhalat n…ôg…ôtun…ôn in neiueiu…ô…ôn.\x - \xo 1:9 \xt 1 Tim 3:2-7; 2 Tim 2:24-26 \x*
\p 
\v 10 Iat…ôghat min-nulan m…ôto-inu net…ômim tep…ôt e nim…ôfak …ôp…ôh Krit kotet…ôhau n…ôg…ôtun…ôn pahrien u. Ilat, n…ôghat…ôn r…ôhalat t…®tat…®per…ôh p…®k tahmen e kalu…ôlu…ô, m…ôto nuhu…ôn lan t…®k…ô, k…ôn moatiuw r…ôk…®s net…ômim neen e n…ôg…ôtun…ôn eiueiu…ô m…®n r…ôhalat. Net…ômim tep…ôt it…ôm koat…ôn m…ôm…ô ok…ôk…ôike k…ôhg-ip…ôn net…ômim, ilat i…ôg…ôtun eiueiu…ô m…®n.\x - \xo 1:10 \xt 1 Tim 4:7 \x*
\v 11 Ahtos…®g-in n…ôghat…ôn r…ôhalat m…ôm…ô ok…ôsot…ôg…ôtun…ôn e nim…ôfak n…ôg…ôtun…ôn …ôh kot…ôrat it…ôm k…ôsot…ôtuat…®p…ôn m…ôm…ô okot…ôg…ôtun, m…ôto-inu n…ôg…ôtun…ôn r…ôhalat tat…ôr…ôk…®n-r…ôk…®n nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôha noanol m…®n rafin r…ôha net…ômim neen. Ilat koat…ôg…ôtun neiueiu…ô…ôn …ôh m…ôto-inu kotolkeike m…ôm…ô okotos m…ôni lan, m…ôto k…ôsotaul…®s…ôn lan.\x - \xo 1:11 \xt 2 Tim 3:5-6; 1 Pita 5:2 \x*
\v 12 Et…ôm Krit kit aup…ôn, in ien kit r…ôhalat, in m…®n t…ôm…ôn min-nulan m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNet…ôm Krit, ilat net…ôm r…ôha neiueiu…ô…ôn nian rafin. K…ôn ilat kotahmen e kuri iarup…®n m…®n. K…ôn ilat n…ôlpah, nian rafin kotolkeike m…ôm…ô kotagw…ôn …ôm lan.‚Äù
\v 13 M…ôto n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha ien u, in tol …ôm n…®pahrien…ôn. K…ôn tol n…ôhlan, …ôhai ilat m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô r…ôhalat n…ôg…ôtun…ôn in neiueiu…ô…ôn, p…ôs ilat okotahat…ôt…ô …ôm e n…ôghat…ôn pahrien,\x - \xo 1:13 \xt 2 Tim 4:2 \x*
\v 14 k…ôn ilat ok…ôsot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn…ôn noanage r…ôha net…ôm Isrel ne n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha net…ôm koatap…ôs n…ôghat…ôn pahrien.\x - \xo 1:14 \xt 1 Tim 4:7 \x*
\v 15 K…ôn n…ôkot…®tun m…ôm…ô net…ômim it…ôm kot…ôtuat…®p e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n, nat t…®k…ô it…ôm otol ilat kotamk…®m…®k. M…ôto net…ômim it…ôm koatamk…®m…®k e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n m…ôto-inu ilat k…ôsotahat…ôt…ô…ôn e Iesu, k…ôn nol…ôn kit t…®k…ô it…ôm otol ilat kot…ôtuat…®p. K…ôn tol min-n…ôhlan, n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn ne n…®kilat k…ôr…ôn k…ôsu…ôtuat…®p…ôn, k…ôn ilat kot…ôruru nakil…ôn nat it…ôm t…ôw…®r, ne nat it…ôm t…ôrat.
\v 16 Ilat koat…ôn m…ôm…ô kot…®tun Uhg…®n, m…ôto nol…ôn r…ôhalat tat…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô koateiu…ô, ilat koat…ôuhlin m…ôntaalat k…ôm Uhg…®n. Net…ôm m…®n …ôh kot…ôrat ag…®n, kotalm…ôl koat…ôht n…ôwia Uhg…®n, k…ôn okol ilat k…ôsotol…ôn nat w…®r kit ne.\x - \xo 1:16 \xt 1 Jon 1:6; 2:4 \x*
\c 2
\s1 N…ôg…ôtun…ôn it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p
\p 
\v 1 M…ôto ik Taetas, ik on…ôk…ôike m…ôg…ôtun w…®r net…ômim e n…ôg…ôtun…ôn it…ôm tat…ôt…ôu-p…ôn n…ôghat…ôn …ôtuat…®p e Iesu.
\v 2 Ik on…ôk…ôike m…ôg…ôtun iagu…®hl m…®n m…ôm…ô e naliw…ôk…ôn r…ôhalat, ilat okotan m…ôt…®g, k…ôn m…ôsot…ôn…®m p…®k…ôn wain, k…ôn nol…ôn r…ôhalat ot…ôk…ôike m…ôtuat…®p w…®r p…ôs net…ômim okot…®siai-in ilat, k…ôn ilat okot…ôk…ôike moat…ôtul …ôskas…®k k…ôn moatol nat…®mnat e nenat…®g…ôn. Nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhalat ot…ôk…ôike mamn…®m w…®r e n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n. K…ôn ilat okot…ôk…ôike motolkeike net…ômim. K…ôn mot…ôk…ôike k…ôtul ti…ôk…®s e nian i…ôk…®s m…®n it…ôm koatuwa e r…ôhalat n…ômeg…ôh…ôn.
\v 3 K…ôn e nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm, n…ôk…ôike m…ôg…ôtun w…®r n…®p…®tagu…®hl m…®n m…ôm…ô ilat okot…ôk…ôike motol nol…ôn it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p m…ôm…ô otos-ip…ôn n…®siaii…ôn k…ôm Uhg…®n. K…ôn ilat ok…ôsot…ôn…ôn n…®kal…® net…ômim. K…ôn s…ôn…ôm…ô n…®p…®tan r…ôha nap…®s…ôn. M…ôto ilat ot…ôk…ôike mot…ôg…ôtun n…ômeg…ôh…ôn …ôtuat…®p.\x - \xo 2:3 \xt 1 Tim 3:11 \x*
\v 4 In…ôh, ilat okot…ôg…ôtun n…®p…®tan m…®n e suat…®p it…ôm ilat okotolkeike r…ôhalat m…®n n…ôman ne nen…ôt…®lat m…®n.
\v 5 Ilat okot…ôk…ôike mot…ôg…ôtun n…®p…®tan m…ôm…ô ilat n…®p…®tan m…ôt…®g it…ôm n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhalat in t…ôtuat…®p, k…ôn ilat k…ôsotan …ôpnap…®n…ôn, k…ôn moat…®siai-in r…ôhalat n…ôman m…®n, k…ôn moatehm w…®r nat…®mnat m…®n r…ôha latu…ônu, k…ôn ilat moatol t…ôw…®r k…ôm net…ômim. Nian koatol nol…ôn tol min-nulan, k…ôn otahtos…®g-in net…ômim m…ôm…ô k…ôsot…ôn rat…ôn n…ôg…ôtun…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n.\x - \xo 2:5 \xt Efes 5:22 \x*
\p 
\v 6 K…ôn e suat…®p kiti…ôh m…®n, ot…ôghat …ôskas…®k k…ôm net…ôm alu…ô m…ôm…ô ilat kot…®tun n…ôn at…®p…ôn e n…®kilat m…ôm…ô kotap…ôs nol…ôn nat…®mnat it…ôm t…ôrat k…ôn moatol …ôm nat it…ôm t…ôw…®r.
\v 7 K…ôn ik, e nat…®mnat rafin, on…ôkol …ôm nat …ôtuat…®p m…®n, p…ôs ilat okot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn nat naka it…ôm ik nakatol. Nian onak…ôg…ôtun, n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôham ot…ôk…ôike m…ôtuat…®p, mol n…ôghat…ôn r…ôham t…ôf…®g…ôm.\x - \xo 2:7 \xt 1 Tim 4:12 \x*
\v 8 Ik onak…ôk…ôike mat…ôn …ôm n…ôghat…ôn pahrien it…ôm net…ômim okol k…ôsot…ôplan…ôn m…ôntaa r…ôham n…ôghat…ôn k…ôn mot…ôn rat. P…ôs in otol r…ôham t…®k…®m…®r m…®n okotaul…®s lan m…ôto-inu ilat k…ôsotehm-p…ôn…ôn nol…ôn rat kit ne lam, k…ôn m…ôsot…ôn…ôn nat t…ôrat kit etat.\x - \xo 2:8 \xt 1 Pita 2:15 \x*
\p 
\v 9 ∆èg…ôtun w…®r slef m…®n m…ôm…ô ilat okotol n…ôwia r…ôhalat et…ôm-iasol m…®n e nat…®mnat rafin, m…ôm…ô n…®kilat otagien o w…ôk r…ôhalat. Slef m…®n ok…ôsot…ôn…ôn n…®tai n…ôghaten r…ôha et…ôm-iasol m…®n r…ôhalat,\x - \xo 2:9 \xt 1 Tim 6:1 \x*
\v 10 k…ôn m…ôsotakl…ôh…ôn k…ôm ilat, m…ôto nian rafin ilat okot…ôk…ôike moatol nat…®mnat …ôtuat…®p m…®n, m…ôm…ô r…ôhalat et…ôm-iasol m…®n okot…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn e r…ôhalat w…ôk. E nol…ôn it…ôm okotol e nat…®mnat rafin, ot…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô n…ôg…ôtun…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n, Iosmeg…ôh r…ôhatat in t…ôtuat…®p m…ôw…®r.
\p 
\v 11 Ik onak…ôk…ôike m…ôg…ôtun nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh rafin m…ôto-inu Uhg…®n t…ômer…ôh r…ôk…®s e suat…®p k…ôm net…ômim rafin m…ôm…ô otosmeg…ôh ilat lan nian t…ôtawte-in r…ôhan n…ôw…®r…ôn k…ôm ilat.
\v 12 N…ôw…®r…ôn …ôh r…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô nian kitat koatat…®g …ôh e n…ôtueint…ôn, kot…ôk…ôike motap…ôs n…ôt…ôu-p…ôn…ôn nol…ôn rat m…®n ne nat…®mnat rat m…®n r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn it…ôm koat…ôwi…ô e n…®kitat, m…ôto okotan m…ôt…®g, k…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhatat ot…ôtuat…®p w…®r motahmen-p…ôn m…ô kitat net…ômim r…ôha Uhg…®n.\x - \xo 2:12 \xt 1 Jon 2:16 \x*
\v 13 N…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhatat in ot…ôk…ôike matol min-nulan nian kitat okoat…ôsahgin nian Iesu Kristo, r…ôhatat Uhg…®n ne r…ôhatat Iosmeg…ôh, in otuwa m…®n lan e n…ôsan…ôn…ôn ne n…ôw…®r…ôn. Nian …ôh in t…ôw…®r ag…®n, k…ôn kitat kot…®tun m…ô ot…ôpanuwa, k…ôn matol n…®kitat t…ôtagien.
\v 14 Iesu n…®kin t…ômagien m…ôm…ô ot…®m…®s otat, k…ôn m…ôtou n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhatat mos-ir…ôk…®s e n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha nol…ôn rat m…®n rafin, k…ôn maf…ôl w…®r kitat m…ôm…ô kitat okotuwa r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim it…ôm kotolkeike m…ôm…ô koatol …ôm nat it…ôm t…ôw…®r.\x - \xo 2:14 \xt Eks 19:5; Dut 7:6; Esik 37:23; Kal 1:4; 1 Pita 2:9 \x*
\p 
\v 15 Nat…®mnat m…®n u, onat…ôg…ôtun ilat e nim…ôfak. L…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhalat m…ôm…ô okoat…ôt…ôu-p…ôn I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, k…ôn m…ôghat …ôskas…®k k…ôm net…ôm koat…ôt…ôu-p…ôn n…ôghat…ôn eiueiu…ô m…®n. Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…®n…ô w…ôk …ôh k…ôm ik, k…ôn …ôghat min-nulan. ∆èsol…ôn m…ôm…ô et…ômim kit ot…ôn rat ik.\x - \xo 2:15 \xt 1 Tim 4:12 \x*
\c 3
\s1 Nol…ôn r…ôha i…ôfak m…®n
\p 
\v 1 Taetas, …ôn-ip…ôn w…®r m…®n k…ôm r…ôham net…ômim m…ôm…ô okot…®siai-in net…ôm-iasol ne kapman r…ôhalat. Okot…ôk…ôike moatol n…ôwialat, k…ôn moat…ôtul mat…®p e nian rafin o nol…ôn w…ôk it…ôm otasitu e net…ômim.\x - \xo 3:1 \xt Rom 13:1-7; 1 Pita 2:13-14 \x*
\v 2 K…ôn ilat ok…ôsot…ôghat eiu…ôn o n…ôr…ôk…®n…ôn n…ôrg…® net…ômim, k…ôn ok…ôsotol…ôn t…®m…ôht, m…ôto ilat nan m…ôt…®g …ôm k…ôn moatol t…ôw…®r k…ôm net…ômim, k…ôn motos-i…ôhau r…ôhalat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn moat…®siai-in net…ômim rafin.
\p 
